00:15:16,583 --> 00:15:18,750
    "Live as if you were to

358
00:15:18,752 --> 00:15:21,019
"die tomorrow.

359
00:15:21,021 --> 00:15:23,554
"Learn as if you were to live

360
00:15:23,556 --> 00:15:24,889
           forever."

